snippet: Cuba's most prominent dissidents say they have been kept in the dark by U.S. officials over a list of 53 political prisoners who will be released from jail as part of a deal to end decades of hostility between the United States and Cuba....

headline.print_headline: In U.S.-Cuba Prisoner Swap, Mystery Surrounds the Unnamed 53
headline.main: In U.S.-Cuba Prisoner Swap, Mystery Surrounds the Unnamed 53

lead_paragraph: Cuba's most prominent dissidents say they have been kept in the dark by U.S. officials over a list of 53 political prisoners who will be released from jail as part of a deal to end decades of hostility between the United States and Cuba.
